Microsoft Graph API Data Extraction Techniques
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Understand Microsoft Graph API authentication and authorization mechanisms
Implement data extraction techniques using Python and Graph API
Apply operational security principles during data collection activities
Analyze detection vectors and implement basic evasion techniques
Document data extraction activities for security assessment purposes
Prerequisites
Basic Python programming knowledge
Understanding of REST APIs and HTTP protocols
Familiarity with OAuth 2.0 authentication concepts
Basic Linux command line skills
Knowledge of JSON data structures
